tions) the most trained and trained men in the country, but in the middle of the way a major accident happens in the ocean and only you survive, so with the thirst of accomplishing the mission you ignore the government's decision to abort the mission and decide to invade the Villa alone and rescue the hostages.<br><br><br>Video and more more information coming soon.<br><br>----------------------------------------------------------<br><br><strong><i>Game and support available in Portuguese and English.</i></strong>",
